snippet.title: Bloody Zombies | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Team up. Bash brains. Save London. Watch the official announce trailer for Bloody Zombies, a new co-op brawler coming to HTC Vive, Oculus Rift, PlayStation VR, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One later this year.

Learn more about Bloody Zombies:

• Website: www.ndreams.com/BloodyZombies
• Facebook: www.facebook.com/BloodyZombies
• Twitter: www.twitter.com/nDreamsVR #BloodyZombies
• Reddit: www.reddit.com/r/ndreams
• Instagram: www.instagram.com/ndreams_vr
